[SPEAKER_10]: upload our quarterly expenditure reports where you can see a full list of projects that we've approved.

400
00:44:22,359 --> 00:44:35,746
[SPEAKER_10]: Yeah, the community survey is a written testimony of the values and needs of the community, so I'd be happy to work to schedule another meeting like this and report on how the future spending goes.

