[SPEAKER_08]: Motion to receive and place on file.

405
00:44:53,817 --> 00:44:59,300
[SPEAKER_11]: On the motion of Vice President Behrs to receive and place on file, seconded by Councilor Carvilla.

406
00:45:00,261 --> 00:45:01,061
