00:49:02,025 --> 00:49:14,672
[SPEAKER_11]: The best way to do that, I have I know I as a counselor have heard from a handful of folks when we first started talking about this that they were very much interested in the reason yes I've heard mixed for many employees and say you know something that's a good idea some don't.

