00:49:15,092 --> 00:49:20,415
[SPEAKER_01]: Some of us it's it's a mix bag and on both on both sides of the argument.

448
00:49:22,694 --> 00:49:25,217
[SPEAKER_01]: how, you know, where the employees stand on.

