00:49:40,481 --> 00:49:53,045
[SPEAKER_05]: Councilor Collins, sorry just a question on that point I had a note from our previous meeting and I wanted to clarify is, um, if we were to enact this would every city employee be automatically opted and I thought I remember that it.

454
00:49:53,726 --> 00:49:58,667
[SPEAKER_05]: You don't have to be on the program, even if Medford were to adopt that is that correct.

455
00:50:01,853 --> 00:50:07,438
[SPEAKER_09]: I think that if this is adopted, then everybody contributes to it.

456
00:50:07,618 --> 00:50:10,020
[SPEAKER_09]: I don't think an employee can opt out of it.

457
00:50:12,742 --> 00:50:13,282
[SPEAKER_05]: That makes sense.

